Near Clemmons / Mile Marker 182 to 182 Heading East. The Contractor for the I-0911A project (I-40 over the Yadkin River at the Davie-Forsyth County Line) will close a ramp at Harper Road (Exit 182) near Clemmons. The contractor will close the off-ramp from I-40 Eastbound to Harper Road from 6:00PM Friday June 18th - 5:00AM Monday June 21st.. This ramp closure is necessary to place asphalt pavement for ramp construction. A detour will be utilized for this ramp closure. A link to the detour map is provided below.&nbsp;This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
